The goal of this project is to build an interactive dashboard using Power BI to:

Analyze sales, profits, and quantity trends

Identify top-performing regions, categories, and sub-categories

Provide actionable business insights for decision-makers

Demonstrate skills in Power BI data modeling, transformation, and visualization

